msg: Applying bug fix from trunk r1305733.

Bug fix. Setting up transaction-timeout="7200" for updateOrderItems service. This problem comes into picture when you have large number of items in an order. For example: Suppose you have more then 100 _different_ items in the cart, each has large quantity and now you wanted to update any of the item quantity then you will observe transaction timeout issue.
